---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Refund Policy — EOB Decoder" description="Refund Policy for EOB Decoder. We offer a 7-day no-questions-asked refund on all purchases.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F7B8C 0%, #2D4A7A 100%);" class="text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-bold mb-4 leading-tight" style="font-size: 40px;">Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-100" style="font-size: 16px;">Last updated: July 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-slate">

      <div class="bg-[#F0FAFB] border border-[#0F7B8C]/20 rounded-xl p-6 mb-10">
        <p class="font-semibold text-[#0F7B8C] mb-2" style="font-size: 18px;">7-Day No-Questions-Asked Refund</p>
        <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed">We stand behind our products. If you are not satisfied with your purchase, you may request a full refund within 7 days of the date of purchase — no questions asked.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">How to Request a Refund</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-4">To request a refund within the 7-day window:</p>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 text-[#334155] leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:amitsharma00261@gmail.com" class="text-[#0F7B8C] hover:underline">amitsharma00261@gmail.com</a> within 7 days of your purchase date.</li>
        <li>Include your order reference number in the subject line or body of the email.</li>
        <li>We will process your refund promptly — no explanation required.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Refunds After 7 Days</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">Refund requests received after the 7-day window will be considered on a case-by-case basis at our discretion. To request a late refund, please email us with your order reference and a brief explanation of your situation. We will do our best to work with you.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Processing Time</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">Approved refunds are typically processed within 5 business days. Depending on your payment method and financial institution, it may take additional time for the funds to appear in your account.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Note on Payment Availability</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">Paid features for EOB Decoder are not yet live. This refund policy is published in advance so you know exactly what to expect when purchases become available.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">For refund requests or questions about this policy, please email: <a href="mailto:amitsharma00261@gmail.com" class="text-[#0F7B8C] hover:underline">amitsharma00261@gmail.com</a></p>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
